{"tid":688102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"給少女2500換做愛？　色翁：我根本不行了","createTime":"2018-06-03T01:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T04:59:52.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b1a6706f260e8a1a929a023c2bfffc7168ceae53","tid":688102,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T01:09:41.000Z","msg":"陳姓老翁誘拐社區1名智能不足的15歲少女，撫摸她胸部、下體，以手指性侵，遭逮辯稱「我根本不行了」。法院認為，陳供詞反覆態度不佳，判1年4個月。<br />\n今日出版的《聯合報》報導，少女供稱，放學在庭園玩都會遇到「色色的阿伯」，騙她說有糖果，結果被帶回對方家。阿伯要她躺在床上，伸手摸胸、下體，再塞2000元要她別跟媽媽講。<br />\n陳坦承知道少女讀國中，表示不清楚她領有身心障礙手冊，有撫摸少女胸部、下體，但一下子而已。法院開庭時，陳卻翻供矢口否認，辯稱少女有說給她2500元就跟他做愛，但自己年紀大了，根本沒辦法。<br />\n檢方調閱監視器，發現陳翁騎機車載她出門，回來後又一起進社區大門，與少女證詞符合。且事發後少女母親曾到派出所要對陳提告，陳還簽下切結書，因此認定他涉有重嫌。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/090929_89288c115dae331991f7c98f11d2d036.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F090929_89288c115dae331991f7c98f11d2d036.png&h=4d2e98e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180603/1366162\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180603%2F1366162&d=vqSqip6ttQbJTQOiRxSQukbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=c80f3485\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180603%2F1366162&h=5367819a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180603/1366162</a>"},{"pid":"0129bd451a238f7525a6075e71eda9cf86fbe06a","tid":688102,"uid":101963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T01:10:28.000Z","msg":"所以話"},{"pid":"9cc590d33729fa2b6db550e00a93d66106327ac7","tid":688102,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T01:12:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/495COzgsnBYl8lYMgu/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.